%A5t-t%E1%BB%8Bch/poem-eiTGchJOdUdBzDCkUFhJYw">Nghi Câu dịch thất tịch - 宜溝驛七夕</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-Ho%C3%A0i-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c/author-il2-xU_Q-nIFla-ypApHCA">Trịnh Hoài Đức</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Ch%C3%AD-Minh/Ng%E1%BB%8D-h%E1%BA%ADu/poem-UByBbFmqwfoB3TCDqFPpnw">Ngọ hậu - 午後</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Ch%C3%AD-Minh/author-a7YEflJr1_rcFKC9dgECgQ">Hồ Chí Minh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/C%E1%BB%91-Qu%C3%BDnh/T%E1%BB%91-trung-t%C3%ACnh/poem-deGxMd7SdB-vRRaf9H5LFw">Tố trung tình - 泝衷情</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/C%E1%BB%91-Qu%C3%BDnh/author-StdXfEfIhxGlKqS3_LVn2w">Cố Quýnh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Nghi-T%C3%B4n/Tu%C3%BD-B%E1%BB%93ng-Lai/poem-YiGy0Yobn2xQlPWYtO-Amg">Tuý Bồng Lai - 醉蓬萊</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Nghi-T%C3%B4n/author-pd7XsJJghP2Tos8AhibgnQ">Vương Nghi Tôn</a>)<br></div>	</div>
